Src
  - package.json
 


 I wanted to upgrade whole(All the package.json file) angular project from 9 to 10
 
 When I execute command __ng update @angular/core@10 @angular/cli@10__  from directory level Lib1 it is still referring to root level package.json file
 I want to start upgradation from Lib1, Lib2, Lib3 but _ng update_ only referring to root level package.json file (Able to upgrade root level project package.json but not child)
 
 Please let me know your thoughts on this.

